  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Donate a Hearing Aid for deaf children in Pakistan</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The rural area Pakistan is very poor, they have limited resources of living. The parents of children with hearing impairment can not afford the purchase of a Hearing Aid for their child because low income &amp; poverty. This project will provide free Hearing Aids to 50 children in one phase then will increase number as per fund raising. The free screening, installation, pre &amp; post speech therapy will be provided at NDF Rehab Center to cover hearing loss.</narrative>
  </description>
